%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20confess%3A%20I%20canceled%20my%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20order.%20But%20not%20for%20the%20reason%20you%20think.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Cybertruck%20at%20Tesla's%20Santana%20Row%20showroom%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%2C%20on%20December%209%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657626730ec98e92f74df3d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Cybertruck%20at%20Tesla's%20Santana%20Row%20showroom%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%2C%20on%20December%209%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EAlistair%20Barr%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20put%20a%20%24100%20reservation%20down%20for%20a%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20in%20June%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETesla%20came%20calling%20about%202%20years%20later.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20why%20I%20couldn't%20pull%20the%20trigger%20on%20a%20purchase.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20car%20nut%20and%20I%20love%20the%20design%20and%20ambition%20of%20Tesla's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-in-person-surprisingly-different-up-close-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECybertruck%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20a%20reservation%20down%20in%20June%202022%2C%20expecting%20to%20be%20so%20far%20back%20in%20line%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-car-sales-slump-salespeople-commission-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20wouldn't%20come%20calling%20for%20years.%20All%20the%20while%2C%20I%20devoured%20online%20reviews%2C%20photos%2C%20and%20videos%20of%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-taking-page-from-ferrari-playbook-with-cybertruck-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20about%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20I%20went%20to%20a%20Tesla%20showroom%20to%20see%20the%20beast%20up%20close%2C%20and%20wrote%20this%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20came%20away%20wanting%20a%20Cybertruck%20more%20than%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20have%20a%20confession%20to%20make%3A%20I%20canceled%20my%20Cybertruck%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c04719b-6e75-4c26-90d5-8bcb397acea9%5C%22%3EA%20lot%20earlier%20than%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20June%2C%20Tesla%20emailed%20me%20to%20say%20it%20was%20ready%20for%20my%20order.%20The%20company%20offered%20me%20the%20chance%20to%20buy%20the%20top%20range%20model%2C%20which%20costs%20more%20than%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20early%20reservation%20holder%2C%20you%20have%20been%20invited%20to%20order%20your%20Foundation%20Series%20Cybertruck%20with%20early%20access%20to%20delivery%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20email%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20that%20struck%20me%20was%20that%20this%20invitation%20came%20in%20a%20lot%20earlier%20than%20I%20expected.%20Back%20in%20the%20pandemic-fueled%20Cybertruck%20reservation%20frenzy%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20super-fans%20sparred%20over%20who%20had%20the%20earliest%20reservations%20and%20crowed%20that%20the%20earliest%20holders%20would%20get%20their%20trucks%203%20or%204%20years%20before%20most%20regular%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20put%20my%20%24100%20reservation%20down%20in%20June%202022%2C%20I%20expected%20to%20get%20the%20call%20from%20Tesla%20in%20mid-2025%20or%202026.%20Right%20now%2C%20I%20just%20don't%20have%20the%20money%20to%20afford%20a%20new%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dbb97dec-b03b-487a-bd33-ccf52213f49e%5C%22%3ETwice%20as%20much%20as%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20was%20likely%20trying%20to%20entice%20me%20into%20buying%20the%20priciest%20Cybertruck%20because%20getting%20%24100%2C000%20for%20each%20vehicle%20sale%20helps%20Tesla%20absorb%20the%20massive%20cost%20of%20ramping%20up%20high-volume%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20again%2C%20I'm%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20afford%20this.%20Back%20in%202022%2C%20I%20naively%20expected%20this%20vehicle%20to%20cost%20about%20%2450%2C000.%20In%202019%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20the%20Cybertruck%20would%20start%20at%20%2440%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I'd%20put%20a%20savings%20plan%20in%20place%20assuming%20I'd%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20roughly%20%2450%2C000%20(probably%20with%20some%20sort%20of%20financing)%20in%20three%20to%20four%20years%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20got%20the%20call%201-to-2%20years%20early%20and%20the%20bill%20was%20twice%20as%20much%20as%20expected.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-cheapest-cybertruck-now-100k-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeapest%20Cybertruck%20is%20almost%20%24100%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d8c31fb-c914-4639-9683-66e70f299a56%5C%22%3EThe%20cost%20of%20college%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20tends%20to%20throw%20other%20curveballs%20at%20you%2C%20too.%20One%20of%20my%20daughters%20is%20off%20to%20college%20soon%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20be%20more%20excited%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20university%20she%20chose%20is%20crushingly%20expensive.%20I%20won't%20go%20into%20details.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20know%20is%20that%20this%20is%20really%20not%20the%20time%20for%20the%20Barr%20family%20to%20be%20spending%20a%20lot%20on%20a%20new%20car.%20That%20was%20the%20final%20nail%20in%20the%20Cybertruck%20coffin%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20colleges%20have%20been%20heavily%20criticized%20for%20becoming%20way%20too%20expensive.%20But%20I'd%20still%20rather%20be%20investing%20(a%20lot!)%20in%20my%20kids'%20education%20than%20shoveling%20money%20into%20a%20brand%20new%20vehicle%2C%20which%20tends%20to%20lose%20value%20pretty%20quickly.%20Even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusks-claim-teslas-appreciate-value-post-purchase-flopped-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETeslas%20depreciate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20what%20Elon%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b7efd158-cdea-4890-a0d0-3ccdeb008a80%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20that%20Cybertrucks%20exist%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20remains%20true%20is%20that%20I%20still%20love%20Tesla%20Cybertrucks.%20I%20still%20want%20one%20badly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesigning%20an%20electric%20pickup%20truck%20with%20very%20few%20compromises%20was%20either%20a%20bold%20inventive%20risk%20or%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20too-powerful%20tech%20executive%20with%20no%20restraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20a%20vehicle%20that%20makes%20me%20smile%20every%20time%20I%20see%20it.%20In%20a%20sea%20of%20Honda%20Accords%20and%20Toyota%20Camrys%2C%20it's%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20words%20of%20one%20of%20my%20Tesla-driving%20neighbors%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20glad%20the%20Cybertruck%20exists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-order-canceled-cost-of-college-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723712402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657626730ec98e92f74df3d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-order-canceled-cost-of-college-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Discover%20how%20other%20priorities%20and%20an%20early%20Tesla%20email%20prompted%20a%20car%20nut%20to%20cancel%20his%20Tesla%20Cybertruck%20order.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-order-canceled-cost-of-college-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It's%20been%20another%20bad%20quarter%20for%20the%20fast-food%20industry.%20Burgers%20and%20pizza%20are%20too%20expensive%2C%20and%20Americans%20just%20don't%20want%20to%20splash%20out.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20meals%20are%20seen%20at%20the%20shopping%20mall%20in%20Krakow%2C%20Poland%20on%20January%2010%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a7b2551a227600e6326bf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcDonald's%2C%20KFC%2C%20and%20Starbucks%20all%20recently%20reported%20drops%20in%20comparable%20US%20sales.%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFast-food%20giants%2C%20including%20McDonald's%2C%20KFC%2C%20and%20Starbucks%2C%20reported%20drops%20in%20comparable%20US%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDiners%20say%20fast%20food%20is%20too%20expensive%20after%20years%20of%20price%20hikes.%20Lower-end%20consumers%20are%20particularly%20cutting%20back.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENot%20enough%20higher-earners%20have%20traded%20down%20into%20the%20category%20to%20offset%20the%20loss%20of%20lower-income%20diners%2C%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20slate%20of%20fast-food%20companies%20have%20reported%20earnings%20over%20the%20last%20three%20weeks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20painting%20a%20bleak%20picture%20of%20the%20American%20consumer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20have%20referred%20to%20%26quot%3Bmore%20cost-conscious%20consumers%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bchallenging%20consumer%20environments%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20in%20many%20cases%20led%20to%20a%20slump%20in%20comparable%20sales%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20McDonald's%2C%20comparable%20US%20sales%20fell%200.7%25%20in%20the%20quarter%20year-over-year%2C%20compared%20to%2010.3%25%20growth%20in%20the%20same%20period%20the%20prior%20year.%20At%20Starbucks%2C%20US%20comparable%20sales%20were%20down%202%25%20in%20the%20quarter%2C%20versus%20the%207%25%20increase%20it%20posted%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FdusZH%2F4%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Change%20in%20comparable%20US%20sales%20at%20fast-food%20chains%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22399%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EKFC%2C%20Papa%20Johns%2C%20Pizza%20Hut%2C%20and%20Firehouse%20Subs%20also%20reported%20a%20drop%20in%20same-store%20sales%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20chains%20including%20Burger%20King%2C%20Popeyes%2C%20and%20Wendy's%2C%20sales%20at%20comparable%20US%20restaurants%20increased%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20in%202023%2C%20but%20at%20a%20much%20slower%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22697c5266-335d-4b1e-a9a6-e46646386dda%5C%22%3ELower-income%20earners%20are%20cutting%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20decline%20in%20comparable%20sales%20is%20simply%20because%20of%20a%20return%20to%20pre-COVID%20operating%20trends%2C%20Jefferies%20restaurant%20analyst%20Andy%20Barish%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20At%20some%20chains%2C%20sales%20boomed%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20consumers%20are%20penny-pinching%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20say%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20they're%20cutting%20back%20on%20fast%20food%20is%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-is-expensive-people-annoyed-eating-out-restaurant-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20such%20good%20value%20for%20money%20anymore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20prices%20of%20both%20groceries%20and%20restaurants%20rose%20at%20accelerated%20rates%20after%20the%20pandemic%20started.%20Grocery%20inflation%20has%20since%20cooled%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-fast-food-is-so-much-more-expensive-value-affordable-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%20at%20fast-food%20restaurants%20is%20still%20above%20pre-pandemic%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20chains%20have%20said%20that%20it's%20lower-end%20consumers%20who%20are%20cutting%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20low-end%20consumer%20has%20continued%20to%20feel%20pressure%20and%20that's%20been%20going%20on%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Barish%20said.%20Some%20are%20placing%20smaller%20fast-food%20orders%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-expensive-americans-cook-at-home-visit-independent-restaurants-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eothers%20are%20buying%20more%20groceries%20instead%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20unusual%20is%20that%20you%20get%20a%20couple%20of%20the%20big%20players%20like%20McDonald's%20and%20Starbucks%20that%20are%20having%20negative%20traffic%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Barish%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20something%20we%20don't%20typically%20see%20even%20in%20these%20kind%20of%20environments%20where%20those%20brands%20would%20be%20typically%20gaining%20share.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdward%20Jones%20analyst%20Brian%20Yarbrough%20told%20BI%20that%20typically%20during%20a%20slowdown%2C%20lower-end%20consumers%20trade%20out%20of%20fast%20food%20while%20middle-%20and%20higher-income%20consumers%20trade%20in%20at%20a%20rate%20that%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%20offsets%26quot%3B%20the%20loss%20of%20lower-earning%20diners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20fast-food%20chains%20have%20raised%20prices%20%26quot%3Bso%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20causing%20the%20gap%20between%20fast-food%20and%20fast-casual%20prices%20to%20shrink%2C%20that%20not%20enough%20higher%20earners%20are%20trading%20down%20into%20fast%20food%20to%20offset%20the%20trade%20out%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20some%20chains%2C%20it%20doesn't%20look%20like%20they%20expect%20spending%20to%20rebound%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20customers%20will%20continue%20to%20feel%20the%20pinch%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20a%20higher%20cost%20of%20living%20for%20at%20least%20the%20next%20several%20quarters%20in%20this%20very%20competitive%20landscape%2C%26quot%3B%20Joe%20Erlinger%2C%20the%20president%20of%20McDonald's%20US%2C%20told%20investors%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20bad%20news%20for%20every%20fast-food%20and%20fast-casual%20chain%2C%20though.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fir.wingstop.com%2Fwingstop-inc-reports-fiscal-second-quarter-2024-financial-results%2F%26sa%3DD%26source%3Deditors%26ust%3D1723214874375739%26usg%3DAOvVaw2uUHbGwp8PqY0ksMQ5LT0N%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWingstop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20said%20that%20same-store%20US%20sales%20grew%2028.7%25%20in%20the%20quarter%2C%20up%20from%2016.8%25%20for%20the%20same%20period%20the%20year%20before.%20Domino's%20and%20Taco%20Bell%20both%20reported%20increases%20in%20comparable%20sales%20growth%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ffd6ab21-9c3f-435f-a95c-9d55274fa635%5C%22%3EConsumers%20want%20value%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BValue%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20word%20on%20restaurant%20executives'%20lips%20this%20summer.%20Joshua%20Kobza%2C%20CEO%20of%20Restaurant%20Brands%20International%2C%20which%20owns%20Burger%20King%2C%20Popeyes%2C%20Tim%20Hortons%2C%20and%20Firehouse%20Subs%2C%20used%20the%20word%20nine%20times%20in%20his%20opening%20remarks%20at%20the%20company's%20August%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast-food%20chains%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20lure%20cash-strapped%20diners%20in%20with%20combo%20deals%20and%20value%20menus.%20It's%20been%20the%20summer%20of%20the%20%245%20deal%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-mcdonalds-5-dollar-meal-deal-pulling-in-customers-inflation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburger-king-launches-5-dollar-value-meal-before-mcdonalds-months-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurger%20King%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kfc.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fkfc-introduces-new-taste-of-kfc-deals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKFC%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20launched%20combo%20deals%20for%20five%20bucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-bundling-breakfast-combo-deals-sandwich-croissant-tea-coffee-meal-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEven%20Starbucks%20is%20getting%20into%20bundling%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarish%2C%20the%20Jefferies%20analyst%2C%20said%20that%20the%20recent%20focus%20on%20value%20menus%20and%20bundled%20meals%20represented%20a%20return%20to%20a%20normal%20pre-COVID%20promotional%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20say%20the%20bundles%20have%20performed%20well%20%E2%80%94%20both%20McDonald's%20and%20Burger%20King%20said%20that%20their%20%245%20deals%20had%20been%20selling%20especially%20well%20among%20lower-income%20consumers%20and%20that%20the%20average%20transaction%20that%20included%20the%20combo%20meal%20came%20to%20more%20than%20%2410%20because%20diners%20added%20other%20items%20to%20their%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20is%20that%20the%20value%20deals%20have%20to%20drive%20enough%20traffic%20to%20offset%20the%20lower%20prices.%20Restaurant%20revenues%20are%20determined%20by%20average%20check%20size%20and%20number%20of%20orders.%20With%20the%20value%20deals%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20got%20to%20drive%20enough%20traffic%20to%20offset%20the%20pricing%20pressure%2C%20and%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20the%20toughest%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20Yarbrough%2C%20the%20Edward%20Jones%20analyst%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20should%20expect%20to%20see%20even%20more%20promotions%20in%20the%20fall%2C%20Northcoast%20Research%20analyst%20Jim%20Sanderson%20told%20BI.%20He%20said%20that%20consumer-packaged%20goods%20c