%3Cli%3EAn%20impressive%20rebound%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20may%20be%20short-lived%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20warns.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUS%20stocks%20are%20pricey%20and%20have%20limited%20upside%2C%20especially%20as%20earnings%20growth%20softens.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHere%20are%2036%20defensive%20stocks%20that%20can%20hold%20up%20if%20markets%20struggle.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20believes%20US%20stocks%20are%20out%20ahead%20of%20their%20skis%20and%20will%20head%20downhill%20from%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20risen%20in%20five%20of%20the%20last%20six%20sessions%20after%20a%20three-day%20market%20bloodbath%20that%20culminated%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-investing-strategy-volatility-economy-earnings-growth-ubs-2024-8%5C%22%3Eworst%20day%20in%20nearly%20two%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%204.8%25%20relief%20rally%20has%20the%20index%20down%20just%201.6%25%20in%20August%20and%20only%204.1%25%20from%20its%20all-time%20high%20set%20in%20mid-July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20leading%20market%20strategists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-stock-market-crash-outlook-investing-strategy-sectors-2024-8%5C%22%3Ethink%20stocks'%20latest%20move%20higher%20is%20sustainable%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks-to-buy-investing-market-outlook-earnings-growth-goldman-sachs-2024-8%5C%22%3Etop%20minds%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20noted%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20tends%20to%20rise%20after%205%25%20drawdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Mike%20Wilson%2C%20who's%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20chief%20US%20equity%20strategist%2C%20warns%20that%20now%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20get%20greedy.%20Even%20if%20stocks%20don't%20enter%20correction%20territory%2C%20the%20investment%20chief%20thinks%20they'll%20likely%20give%20up%20some%20of%20their%20recent%20gains%20and%20stay%20in%20no%20man's%20land%2C%20potentially%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20will%20trade%20between%205%2C000%20(19x)%20and%205%2C400%20(20.5x)%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20until%20we%20have%20evidence%20of%20either%20better%20or%20worse%20growth%20or%20we%20get%20a%20policy%20response%20that%20either%20satisfies%20or%20disappoints%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20wrote%20in%20an%20August%2012%20note.%20%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20at%20the%20upper%20end%20of%20that%20band%2C%20we%20see%20risks%20weighted%20to%20the%20downside%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStocks%20are%20too%20expensive%20as%20earnings%20fade%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20late-summer%20stretch%2C%20investors%20are%20awaiting%20answers%20to%20several%20key%20questions%2C%20including%20how%20strong%20the%20US%20economy%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funemployment-rate-job-growth-july-labor-market-economic-data-2024-7%5C%22%3Elabor%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%2C%20how%20much%20interest%20rates%20will%20fall%2C%20who%20will%20win%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%2C%20and%20what%20the%20policy%20priorities%20from%20the%20next%20administration%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20cautious%20near-term%20outlook%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20still%20doesn't%20see%20a%20recession%20coming.%20However%2C%20Wilson%20expects%20the%20expansion%20to%20continue%20at%20a%20slower%20pace%2C%20noting%20that%20economic%20fundamentals%20have%20weakened%20since%20April.%20In%20this%20backdrop%2C%20earnings%20growth%20will%20be%20more%20tepid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222162%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MS%20economic%20surprises%20since%20April%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bbf90d955b01c3294e62a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221038%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3