t%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eruling%20describing%20Google%20as%20a%20monopoly%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20have%20other%20big%20tech%20companies%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20nearly%20300-page%20ruling%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20Amit%20Mehta%20wrote%20that%20parent%20company%20Alphabet's%20deals%20to%20make%20Google%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20other%20platforms%20violated%20corporate%20competition%20laws%20while%20accruing%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20is%20a%20monopolist%2C%20and%20it%20has%20acted%20as%20one%20to%20maintain%20its%20monopoly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mehta%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Justice%20is%20now%20mulling%20whether%20to%20seek%20a%20potential%20breakup%20of%20the%20company%2C%20Bloomberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-08-13%2Fdoj-considers-seeking-google-goog-breakup-after-major-antitrust-win%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20previously%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20appeal%20Judge%20Mehta's%20ruling%2C%20and%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%3Edecision%20%26quot%3Brecognizes%20that%20Google%20offers%20the%20best%20search%20engine%2C%20but%20concludes%20that%20we%20shouldn't%20be%20allowed%20to%20make%20it%20easily%20available.%26quot%3B%20Business%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20company%20for%20any%20further%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Google%20on%20its%20heels%20%E2%80%94%20the%20developments%20are%20a%20clear%20signal%20to%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-trial-big-tech-future-analysis-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20that%20they%20should%20be%20worried%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Big%20Tech%20has%20lost%20an%20antitrust%20suit%20and%20faced%20a%20potential%20split.%20Microsoft%20was%20ruled%20a%20monopoly%20in%20t