%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20using%20its%20retail%20dominance%20to%20squeeze%20third-party%20sellers%20on%20its%20platform%2C%20and%20Meta%20amid%20its%20attempts%20to%20dominate%20the%20social%20media%20market%20through%20acquisitions%20like%20Instagram%20and%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20cases%20are%20resource-intensive%2C%20have%20little%20precedent%2C%20and%20are%20the%20most%20ambitious%20antitrust%20lawsuits%20in%20decades.%20One%20big%20consequence%20of%20the%20Google%20ruling%20is%20it%20will%20give%20federal%20agencies%20a%20boost%20of%20confidence%20that%20the%20risk%20is%20worth%20it%2C%20according%20to%20former%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20chair%20William%20Kovacic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20huge%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20to%20your%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Kovacic%2C%20now%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20George%20Washington%20University%20Law%20School%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20your%20success%20in%20all%20these%20other%20matters%20involves%20having%20more%20people%20fully%20committed%20and%20willing%20to%20work%20their%20fingers%20to%20the%20bone%20to%20make%20this%20work.%20Judge%20Mehta's%20ruling%20suggests%20that%20the%20sacrifice%2C%20the%20effort%2C%20is%20worth%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Amazon%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22529e4ba3-de45-4723-b58d-c645fcd05336%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20a%20'market%2C'%20anyway%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20win%20an%20antitrust%20case%2C%20plaintiffs%20need%20to%20prove%20that%20a%20particular%20company%20illegally%20dominates%20a%20particular%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20the%20cases%20get%20stuck%20on%20the%20question%20of%20how%20to%20define%20a%20particular%20market%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefendants%20typically%20define%20the%20market%20broadly%2C%20arguing%20they're%20just%20one%20fish%20in%20a%20big%20pond.%20Plaintiffs%20try%20to%20define%20the%20market%20in%20narrow%20terms%2C%20arguing%20the%20companies%20are%20such%20big%20fish%20that%20they%20are%20illegally%20taking%20up%20space%20in%20a%20very%20small%20pond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20previously%20tossed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Meta%20over%20these%20ambiguities%2C%20ruling%20that%20regulators%20didn't%20sufficiently%20define%20the%20social%20media%20market%20that%20the%20FTC%20alleged%20Meta%20monopolized%20before%20the%20regulator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fruling-ftc-meta-facebook-lawsuit-instagram-whatsapp-can-proceed-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erefiled%20its%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25042101-judge-amit-mehta-google-alphabet-antitrust-monopoly-decision%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJudge%20Mehta's%20mammoth%20Google%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20judges%20exactly%20how%20to%20handle%20the%20market-definition%20puzzle%2C%20according%20to%20Bill%20Baer%2C%20a%20former%20top%20antitrust%20lawyer%20at%20the%20Justice%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20used%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-1990s-antitrust-case-looms-over-apple-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elandmark%202001%20United%20States%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20decision%20against%20Microsoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20demonstrated%20how%20its%20findings%20could%20be%20mapped%20onto%20Alphabet's%20conduct%20to%20dominate%20the%20search%20market%20for%20Google.%20That%20same%20strategy%20could%20be%20used%20by%20other%20judges%20overseeing%20cases%20against%20Amazon%2C%20Apple%2C%20or%20other%20tech%20companies%2C%20Baer%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20analytical%20process%20of%20figuring%20out%20what%2C%20in%20real%20terms%2C%20competes%20with%20other%20things%2C%20and%20not%20let%20the%20defendant%20kind%20of%20throw%20spaghetti%20at%20the%20wall%20and%20see%20what%20sticks%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20the%20Google%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Baer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20normally%20hire%20econometricians%20to%20create%20big%2C%20complicated%20models%20to%20define%20big%2C%20complicated%20markets%2C%20according%20to%20Rebecca%20Allensworth%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20antitrust%20law%20at%20Vanderbilt%20University%20Law%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20expensive%2C%20resource-intensive%20approach%20to%20defining%20markets%20for%20these%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMehta%2C%20however%2C%20adopted%20a%20more%20commensensical%20standard%2C%20favored%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20complex%20mathematical%20models%2C%20Mehta%20looked%20at%20internal%20documents%2C%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20businesses%20themselves%2C%20and%20testimony%20from%20rival%20companies%20to%20define%20the%20%26quot%3Bsearch%20market%26quot%3B%20Google%20monopolized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20other%20judges%20follow%20suit%20and%20follow%20the%20same%20standard%2C%20it%20could%20lower%20the%20bar%20for%20bringing%20antitrust%20lawsuits%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20bar%20is%20you%20have%20to%20prove%20this%20to%20a%20mathematical%20certainty%2C%20you're%20just%20going%20to%20throw%20out%20a%20lot%20of%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20Allensworth%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223cb9553c-a301-4918-a33c-ccbe70c612b4%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20may%20be%20more%20cautious%20about%20acquisitions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20may%20not%20be%20rushing%20to%20change%20their%20entire%20business%20models%2C%20but%20the%20recent%20court%20decision%20could%20make%20them%20more%20cautious%20about%20acquisitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Google%20ruling%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20regulators%20will%20face%20success%20pursuing%20similar%20judgments%20against%20other%20tech%20giants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolfe%20Research%20analyst%20Shweta%20Khajuria%20told%20BI%20Google's%20lawsuit%20may%20be%20different%20from%20other%20Big%20Tech%20players%20because%20Google%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20more%20dominant%20presence%26quot%3B%20in%20Search%20than%20any%20other%20company%20has%20in%20its%20respective%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20still%20competes%20with%20Snapchat%20and%20TikTok%2C%20Khajuria%20said.%20But%20the%20Google%20lawsuit%20is%20significant%20because%20it's%20%26quot%3Bby%20far%20the%20biggest%26quot%3B%20antitrust%20case%2C%20and%20it%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20bellwether%20for%20other%20companies%2C%20Khajuria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20underlying%20takeaway%20is%20that%20no%20company%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20big%20they%20are%2C%20is%20above%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Khajuria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmarketer%20analyst%20Max%20Willens%20isn't%20convinced%20that%20the%20ruling%20should%20make%20other%20tech%20giants%20concerned.%20He%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20ruling%20against%20Google%20%26quot%3Bshouldn't%20necessarily%20signal%20that%20these%20other%20companies%26quot%3B%20are%20in%20bad%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20lawsuits%20involve%20very%20different%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20Willens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20difference%20in%20lawsuits%2C%20Willens%20also%20said%20Google%20will%20%26quot%3Bvigorously%20defend%20itself%26quot%3B%20and%20appeal%20the%20decision%2C%20which%20will%20probably%20delay%20the%20final%20verdict%20by%20years.%20Until%20the%20final%20verdict%20comes%20out%2C%20companies%20aren't%20going%20to%20preemptively%20change%20their%20businesses%2C%20Willens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20change%20of%20pace%20to%20Big%20Tech%2C%26quot%3B%20Willens%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20new%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20cause%20them%20to%20take%20a%20measure%20so%20drastic%20that%20it%20would%20impair%20their%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhajuria%20also%20said%20she%20doesn't%20anticipate%20companies%20taking%20proactive%20action%20to%20prevent%20a%20similar%20outcome.%20However%2C%20she%20said%20the%20tech%20giants%20might%20be%20more%20cautious%20about%20making%20large%20acquisitions%20that%20could%20draw%20attention%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIves%20also%20said%20that%20it's%20unlikely%20business%20models%20will%20dramatically%20change%2C%20but%20he%20said%20the%20decision%20may%20push%20Apple%20to%20settle%20its%20lawsuit%20before%20it%20goes%20to%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIves%20wrote%20in%20a%20Wedbush%20note%20to%20investors%20that%20although%20the%20case%20is%20expected%20to%20last%20for%20years%2C%20he%20predicted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-antitrust-lawsuit-doj-timeline-wedbush-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettlement%20will%20likely%20be%20reached%20in%20the%20next%2012%20to%2018%20months%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20clear%20that%20Judge%20Mehta's%20decision%20in%20the%20Alphabet%20cases%20has%20pierced%20any%20perception%20that%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20with%20their%20high-powered%20lawyers%20and%20massive%20resources%20%E2%80%94%20are%20invincible%20in%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20vibe%2C%20and%20that's%20really%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Allensworth%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20sense%20that%20in%20a%20very%20high%20profile%20case%2C%20by%20a%20very%20thoughtful%2C%20legalistic%2C%20kind%20of%20nonpartisan%20judge%20saying%20that%20this%20Big%20Tech%20company%20is%20a%20monopolist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bombshell%20ruling%20like%20that%20is%20bound%20to%20make%20the%20other%20tech%20giants%20sit%20up%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-monopoly-antitrust-ruling-should-make-apple-meta-amazon-nervous-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723709222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insid