tstimes.com%2Fasia%2Feast-asia%2Fseoul-authorities-find-toxic-substances-in-shein-and-temu-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20AFP%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%20quantities%20of%20phthalates%2C%20a%20chemical%20compound%20that%20makes%20plastics%20more%20flexible%2C%20were%20found%20in%20some%20pairs%20of%20Shein%20shoes.%20The%20authorities%20told%20the%20AFP%20that%20one%20particular%20pair%20had%20229%20times%20the%20legal%20limit%20for%20phthalates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPhthalate-based%20plasticizers%20affect%20reproductive%20functions%20such%20as%20sperm%20count%20reduction%20and%20can%20cause%20infertility%20and%20even%20premature%20birth%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20from%20Seoul's%20environmental%20health%20team%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20also%20told%20AFP%20that%20products%20from%20Temu%20contained%20higher-than-permissible%20levels%20of%20toxic%20substances.%20Sandal%20insoles%20sold%20by%20the%20online%20marketplace%20contained%2011%20times%20more%20lead%20than%20legally%20permissible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Temu%20told%20BI%3A%20%26quot%3BUpon%20receiving%20notice%20from%20the%20Seoul%20city%20government%2C%20we%20immediately%20launched%20an%20internal%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20the%2011%20products%20identified%2C%20two%20items%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pair%20of%20sandals%20and%20a%20hat%20%E2%80%94%20were%20from%20Temu%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20swiftly%20removed%20these%20product%20listings%20from%20our%20global%20marketplace%20and%20are%20enhancing%20our%20systems%20and%20guidance%20to%20merchants%20to%20ensure%20they%20comply%20with%20safety%20standards%20and%20local%20regulations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Shein's%20products%20have%20been%20flagged%20in%20South%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20investigation%20in%20May%2C%20Seoul%20government%20officials%20said%20t