nvoking%20the%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3Bdivine%20wrath%26quot%3B.%20This%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20growing%20tensions%20between%20Iran%20and%20Israel%20following%20the%20assassination%20of%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%2C%20the%20political%20chief%20of%20Hamas%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20last%20month%20during%20an%20official%20visit%20to%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhamenei's%20remarks%20condemned%20what%20he%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Benemy%20psychological%20warfare%26quot%3B%20aimed%20at%20pressuring%20Iran%20to%20reconsider%20any%20plans%20for%20retaliation%20against%20Israel.%20The%2086-year-old%20said%20that%20any%20retreat%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20military%2C%20political%2C%20or%20economic%2C%20would%20invite%20severe%20divine%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaniyeh's%20death%2C%20which%20Tehran%20attributes%20to%20Israeli%20intelligence%2C%20has%20since%20placed%20Iran%20in%20a%20precarious%20position%20as%20it%20deliberates%20over%20the%20timing%20and%20nature%20of%20its%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernments%20that%20yield%20to%20the%20demands%20of%20today's%20dominant%20powers%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20nation's%20size%20or%20strength%2C%20can%20defy%20these%20pressures%20if%20they%20draw%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20their%20people%20and%20accurately%20assess%20their%20adversaries'%20true%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20Khamenei%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iranintl.com%2Fen%2F202408148230%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20Iran%20International.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayatollah%20also%20criticised%20the%20longstanding%20tendency%20to%20exaggerate%20the%20power%20of%20enemies%2C%20citing%20historical%20examples%20of%20US%2C%20British%2C%20and%20Israeli%20attempts%20to%20undermine%20Iran%20since%20the%201979%20Islamic%20Revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20heated%20rhetoric%2C%20Iran%20has%20refrained%20from%20immediate%20retaliation%2C%20a%20move%20seen%20by%20some%20analysts%20as%20a%20strategic%