that%20the%20waiter%20was%20negligent%20and%20demanded%20damages%20over%20%2450%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisney%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20argued%20that%20the%20case%20should%20be%20dismissed%20and%20settled%20out%20of%20court%20because%20Mr%20Piccolo%20had%20agreed%20to%20the%20company's%20terms%20of%20use%20when%20he%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20one-month%20free%20trial%20of%20Disney%2B%20in%202019%20and%20in%202023.%20Disney%20says%20the%20terms%20state%20that%20users%20of%20Disney's%20service%20agree%20to%20settle%20any%20disputes%20with%20the%20company%20out%20of%20court%20via%20arbitration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20create%20a%20Disney%2B%20or%20ESPN%2B%20account%2C%20you%20also%20agree%20to%20the%20Walt%20Disney%20Company's%20Terms%20of%20Use%2C%20which%20govern%20your%20use%20of%20other%20Disney%20Services.%20The%20services%20include%20sites%2C%20software%2C%20applications%2C%20content%2C%20product%20and%20services%2C%20which%20include%20the%20Disney%20Parks%20and%20Resorts%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisney%20has%20argued%20that%20these%20terms%20of%20use%20include%20a%20clause%20that%20applies%20to%20%E2%80%9Call%20disputes%E2%80%9D%20including%20those%20involving%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Walt%20Disney%20Company%20or%20its%20affiliates%E2%80%9D%20of%20which%20Walt%20Disney%20Parks%20and%20Resorts%20is%20a%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723704900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fa5o0daoo_disney-merchandise_625x300_19_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-agreed-to-disney-terms-disney-after-man-sues-it-for-wifes-death-6342338%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Subscription%20to%20a%20free%20one%20month%20trial%20of%20Disney%2B%20is%20the%20reason%20a%20man%20cannot%20sue%20after%20his%20wife%20died%20from%20eating%20at%20Disney%20World%20resort%2C%20the%20company's%20lawyers%20argued.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22cano