nts%20against%20Mr%20Rajput.%20The%20complaints%20were%20related%20to%20the%20illegal%20occupation%20and%20construction%20on%20their%20ancestral%20land%20in%20Sagar%20district%2C%20allegedly%20by%20the%20minister%20and%20his%20associates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Mansingh%20Patel%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Mansingh%20Patel%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ftmdsc68_mansingh-patel-_625x300_15_August_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansingh%20Patel%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitaram%20Patel%20further%20alleged%20that%20his%20father's%20disappearance%20was%20likely%20a%20result%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20silence%20him%20and%20seize%20the%20valuable%20property.%20Despite%20multiple%20complaints%20to%20local%20authorities%20and%20the%20CM%20Helpline%2C%20no%20substantial%20police%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20trace%20Mansingh%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20OBC%20Mahasabha%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20took%20cognizance%20of%20the%20case%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20allegations%20and%20the%20involvement%20of%20politically%20influential%20individuals.%20The%20petitioners%20sought%20a%20writ%20of%20Habeas%20Corpus%20to%20produce%20Mansingh%20Patel%20before%20the%20court%2C%20alleging%20illegal%20detention%20and%20potential%20criminality%20by%20the%20respondents%2C%20including%20Mr%20Rajput.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20during%20the%20hearing%2C%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20progress%20in%20the%20investigation%20by%20the%20local%20police%20and%20directed%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20of%20Sagar%20district%2C%20to%20submit%20a%20detailed%20affidavit%20outlining%20the%20chronological%20developments%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20despite%20the%20serious%20nature%20of%20the%20allegations%2C%20the%20local%20police%20had%20failed%20to%20conduct%20a%20fair%2C%20independent%2C%20and%20thorough%20investigation%2C%20further%20criticizing%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20initial%20SIT%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20inadequate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20to%20constitute%20a%20new%20SIT%20comprising%20senior%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officers%20from%20outside%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIT%20is%20mandated%20to%20re-investigate%20the%20disappearance%20of%20Mansingh%20Patel%2C%20with%20the%20following%20key%20directives%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20ordered%20that%20the%20Missing%20Person%20Complaint%20be%20immediately%20registered%20as%20an%20FIR%2C%20initially%20against%20unknown%20persons%2C%20to%20ensure%20the%20investigation%20is%20conducted%20with%20due%20seriousness.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20SIT%20was%20instructed%20to%20provide%20protection%20to%20witnesses%20and%20ensure%20that%20their%20statements%20are%20recorded%20in%20a%20conducive%20environment%2C%20with%20video%20documentation%20and%2C%20where%20necessary%2C%20under%20Section%20164%20of%20the%20Cr.P.C.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20investigation%20must%20also%20include%20a%20thorough%20examination%20of%20revenue%20records%20related%20to%20the%20disputed%20land%2C%20identifying%20the%20actions%20that%20led%20to%20the%20disappearance%20of%20Mansingh%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIT%20is%20required%20to%20complete%20the%20investigation%20within%20four%20months%2C%20after%20which%20further%20legal%20actions%20will%20follow%20based%20on%20the%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20police%20stated%20that%20between%20September%202017%20to%20September%202019%2C%20it%20visited%20various%20places%20to%20locate%20the%20missing%20person%2C%20but%20in%20vain.%20The%20top%20court%20rejected%20the%20contentions%20of%20the%20state%20against%20the%20plea's%20maintainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%2C%20however%2C%20not%20impressed%20by%20the%20objection.%20The%20reporting%20of%20the%20commission%20of%20a%20cognizable%20offence%20is%20a%20statutory%20obligation%20on%20one%20and%20all.%20Where%20such%20reporting%20has%20been%20discarded%20by%20the%20police%2C%20deliberately%20or%20otherwise%2C%20the%20vigilant%20section%20of%20society%20or%20social%20help%20groups%20are%20expected%20to%20espouse%20such%20cause%20for%20securing%20justice%20to%20the%20voiceless%20victims%20and%2For%20those%20who%20have%20been%20silenced%20under%20mysterious%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwing%20to%20the%20serious%20nature%20of%20allegations%20against%20the%20influential%2C%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20existing%20SIT%20by%20the%20State%20is%20a%20mere%20eye-wash%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20won't%20be%20possible%20at%20all%20for%20that%20SIT%20to%20take%20the%20investigation%20to%20a%20logical%20conclusion%20which%20can%20inspire%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20family%2C%20near%20and%20dear%20ones%20of%20the%20victim%20or%20the%20public%20in%20general.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723699800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fhb3etd9_govind-singh-rajput-_625x300_15_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-impact-probe-team-ordered-over-ministers-role-in-disappearance-6341890%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ordered%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20to%20probe%20the%20mysterious%20disappearance%20of%20Mansingh%20Patel%2C%20a%20case%20that%20garnered%20significant%20attention%20following%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20on%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-impact-probe-team-ordered-over-ministers-role-in-disappearance-6341890%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampU