(a%20town%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh)%20for%20four%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ajay%20elaborates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%E2%80%99d%20been%20warned%20of%20bad%20weather%20and%20landslides.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%201%20am%20and%20a%20landslide%20hit%20the%20road.%20The%20driver%20suggested%20we%20turn%20back%20and%20stay%20in%20a%20nearby%20town%20for%20the%20night.%20But%20as%20we%20made%20our%20way%20back%2C%20another%20landslide%20hit.%20We%20were%20trapped%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20parallels%20with%20this%20situation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F155022%2Futtarakhand-dharchula-flood-bridge-landslide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20landslides%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20had%20previously%20witnessed%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20you%20see%20people%20getting%20down%20from%20their%20vehicles%20and%20attempting%20to%20move%20the%20rocks.%20But%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20boulders%20that%20had%20fallen%20were%20twice%20the%20size%20of%20a%20JCB%20Backhoe%20Loader.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftravel-1-1723198486.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ajay%20and%20Angelica%20drove%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Thang%20in%20Ladakh%20in%202023%20covering%207000%20km%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftravel-1-1723198486.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftravel-1-1723198486-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftravel-1-1723198486-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftravel-1-1723198486-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftravel-1-1723198486-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360529%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAjay%20and%20Angelica%20drove%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Thang%20in%20Ladakh%20in%202023%20covering%207000%20km%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ajay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20take%20days%20for%20the%20debris%20to%20be%20cleared.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20given%20a%20space%20in%20a%20hotel%E2%80%99s%20restaurant%20next%20to%20the%20tables%20where%20the%20owner%20put%20up%20a%20few%20makeshift%20beds%20and%20blankets.%20But%20we%20were%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20for%20four%20days%20with%20very%20little%20food%20and%20water%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20no%20electricity%20and%20internet.%E2%80%9D%20Ajay%20adds%20that%20the%20warmth%20of%20the%20locals%20compensated%20for%20these%20tough%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20they%20would%20prepare%20something%20they%E2%80%99d%20invite%20us%20to%20eat%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Finally%2C%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%2C%20the%20duo%20managed%20to%20make%20it%20out%20safely%20and%20reach%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20experiences%20are%20scary%2C%20Angelica%20says%20they%20strengthened%20the%20bond%20she%20shares%20with%20her%20father.%20Grateful%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335201%2Fliving-with-rheumatoid-arthritis-inspiring-story-of-adventure-on-river-ganga%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epartake%20in%20adventures%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20many%20others%20her%20age%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20fortune%20of%2C%20Angelica%20does%20not%20take%20her%20luck%20lightly.%20%E2%80%9CLike%20any%20other%20teenager%2C%20I%20sometimes%20regarded%20my%20father%20as%20unreasonable.%20But%20these%20trips%20have%20made%20me%20appreciate%20how%20his%20brain%20works%2C%