%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramaswamy%20went%20on%20to%20explain%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20quota%20system%2C%20which%20was%20implemented%20after%20the%201971%20war%20that%20saw%20Bangladesh%20gain%20independence%20from%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBangladesh%20fought%20a%20bloody%20war%20for%20its%20independence%20in%201971.%20Hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Bangladeshi%20civilians%20were%20raped%20and%20murdered.%20It%20was%20a%20tragedy%2C%20and%20it%20was%20rightly%20mourned.%20But%20in%20its%20aftermath%2C%20Bangladesh%20implemented%20a%20quota%20system%20for%20jobs%20in%20their%20civil%20service%3A%2080%25%20of%20the%20jobs%20were%20allocated%20to%20specific%20social%20groups%20(war%20veterans%2C%20rape%20victims%2C%20underrepresented%20residents%2C%20etc.)%2C%20and%20only%2020%25%20were%20allocated%20based%20on%20merit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20turmoil%20in%20Bangladesh%20reached%20a%20climax%20on%20August%205%2C%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20aged%2076%2C%20fled%20the%20country%20by%20helicopter%20to%20India%20as%20protesters%20overran%20the%20streets%20of%20Dhaka.%20Her%2015-year%20rule%2C%20marked%20by%20allegations%20of%20human%20rights%20abuses%2C%20came%20to%20a%20dramatic%20end.%20The%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20her%20ousting%20were%20bloody%2C%20with%20more%20than%20450%20dying%20during%20the%20unrest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20quota%20system%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20disaster%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramaswamy%20claimed%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%202018%20protests%20that%20led%20Bangladesh%20to%20scrap%20most%20of%20the%20quotas%2C%20only%20for%20them%20to%20be%20reinstated%20in%202024.%20The%20Indian-origin%20politician%20warned%20that%20such%20systems%2C%20designed%20to%20rectify%20past%20wrongs%2C%20can%20inadvertently%20perpetuate%20cycles%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20chaos%20begins%2C%20it%20can't%20easily%20be%20reined%20in.%20Radicals%20are%20now%20targeting%20Hindu%20minorities.%20A%20quota%20conflict%20created%20to%20rectify%20the%20wrongs%20of%20rape%20and%20violence%20in%201971%20is%20now%20leading%20to%20more%20rape%20and%20violence%20in%202024.%20Bloodshed%20is%20the%20endpoint%20of%20grievance%20and%20victimhood.%20It's%20hard%20not%20to%20look%20at%20Bangladesh%20and%20wonder%20what%20lessons%20we%20would%20do%20well%20to%20learn%20right%20here%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20Ms%20Hasina's%20Awami%20League%20party%20went%20into%20hiding%2C%20and%20the%20country%20plunged%20into%20further%20instability.%20According%20to%20reports%20from%20the%20Bangladesh%20Hindu%20Buddhist%20Christian%20Unity%20Council%20and%20the%20Bangladesh%20Puja%20Udjapan%20Parishad%2C%20there%20have%20been%20at%20least%20205%20incidents%20of%20attacks%20on%20minority%20communities%20across%2052%20districts%20since%20Ms%20Hasina's%20departure.%20Thousands%20of%20Bangladeshi%20Hindus%20have%20sought%20refuge%20in%20India%2C%20fearing%20for%20their%20safety%20in%20the%20volatile%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723692000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F6jgbfcqo_vivek-ramaswamy-afp-_625x300_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftargeted-violence-against-hindus-vivek-ramaswamy-on-bangladesh-unrest-6341207%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20has%20spoken%20out%20strongly%20against%20attacks%20on%20the%20Hindu%20minority%20community%20in%20Bangladesh%20during%20the%20recent%20political%20unrest%20in%20the%20country%20following%20the%20ouster%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftargeted-violence-against-hindus-vivek-ramaswamy-on-bangladesh-unrest-6341207%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%