com%2Fsam-altman-chatgpt-openai-ceo-career-net-worth-ycombinator-prepper-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Fortune%20Magazine%20in%202023%20that%20he%20believed%20one%20of%20the%20tech%20industry's%20%26quot%3Bworst%20mistakes%26quot%3B%20was%20to%20allow%20employees%20to%20go%20%26quot%3Bfull%20remote%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20that%20the%20experiment%20on%20that%20is%20over%2C%20and%20the%20technology%20is%20not%20yet%20good%20enough%20that%20people%20can%20be%20full%20remote%20forever%2C%20particularly%20on%20startups%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20still%20implements%20a%20mix%20of%20hybrid%20and%20remote%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20OpenAI%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20requires%20its%20in-person%20employees%20to%20come%20to%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week%20while%20also%20maintaining%20some%20remote%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20a%20similar%20policy%20requiring%20most%20workers%20to%20come%20in%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.google%2Fbelonging%2Fdiversity-annual-report%2F2022%2Fflexibility%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20blog%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Google%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-ceo-marc-benioff-remote-work-rto-mandate-policy-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalesforce%20CEO%20Marc%20Benioff%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20once%20proclaimed%20himself%20to%20be%20a%20chronic%20remote%20worker%2C%20also%20touted%20the%20belief%20that%20some%20employees%20need%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20need%20to%20mix%20in-person%20and%20remote%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Benioff%20said.%20%2