0have%20full%20protection%20in%20those%20situations%2C%26quot%3B%20Bowersox%20told%20BI%20during%20the%20press%20briefing.%20%26quot%3BThose%20are%20the%20types%20of%20things%20that%20raise%20the%20risk%20level%20and%20complicate%20our%20decision%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ee056bc-2980-4a24-8469-c9195f394106%5C%22%3EWhy%20NASA%20hasn't%20made%20a%20decision%20yet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20NASA%20is%20taking%20the%20time%20to%20run%20its%20data%20and%20options%20through%20three%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20authorities%3A%26quot%3B%20a%20chief%20engineer%2C%20a%20chief%20health%20and%20medical%20officer%2C%20and%20a%20chief%20of%20safety%20and%20mission%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20has%20also%20brought%20in%20%26quot%3Bnew%20propulsion%20system%20experts%26quot%3B%20to%20give%20feedback%2C%20Bowersox%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20those%20various%20reviews%20are%20complete%2C%20the%20agency%20will%20complete%20a%20flight%20readiness%20review%20with%20representatives%20from%20across%20the%20agency%20and%20make%20its%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20very%20hyper-focused%20lately%20on%20this%20concept%20of%20combating%20organizational%20silence.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20both%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20Challenger%20and%20Columbia%2C%20you%20can%20see%20cases%20where%20people%20had%20the%20right%20data%20or%20a%20valid%20position%20to%20put%20forward%2C%20but%20the%20environment%20just%20didn't%20allow%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Russ%20DeLoach%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20NASA's%20Office%20of%20Safety%20and%20Mission%20Assurance%20%E2%80%94%20the%20third%20technical%20authority%20%E2%80%94%20said%20in%20the%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recognize%20that%20that%20may%20mean%2C%20at%20times%2C%20we%20don't%20move%20very%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWillams'%20and%20Wilmore's%20mission%2C%20which%20is%20Starliner's%20first%20crewed%20test%20flight%2C%20was%20supposed%20to%20last%20about%20eight%20days%