%20million%20trees%20across%20the%20country%20and%20rejuvenated%20six%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20founder%20to%20learn%20how%20he%20has%20achieved%20this%20feat%20through%20community%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETo%20revive%20Bengaluru%20to%20its%20initial%20glory%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20in%20detail%20about%20his%20motivation%20to%20start%20SayTrees%2C%20the%20software%20engineer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20roads%20were%20covered%20with%20giant%20trees.%20The%20cover%20was%20so%20dense%20that%20one%20could%20not%20see%20the%20sun.%20One%20day%20when%20I%20was%20travelling%20from%20home%20to%20office%2C%20I%20was%20as%20usual%20looking%20at%20the%20tall%20trees%20on%20the%20roads.%20The%20other%20morning%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20all%20those%20trees%20were%20gone.%20It%20was%20disheartening%20for%20me%20as%20I%20valued%20them%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20trees%20were%20being%20chopped%20down%20for%20road%20widening%20and%20metro%20construction.%20Although%20the%20Government%20was%20transplanting%20them%2C%20I%20felt%20responsible%20as%20a%20citizen.%20Otherwise%2C%20Bengaluru%20would%20become%20like%20any%20other%20Indian%20city.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20regret%20later%20that%20I%20could%20have%20done%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20began%20visiting%20government%20offices%20to%20understand%20his%20role%20and%20capacity%20as%20a%20citizen.%20In%202007%2C%20he%20started%20planting%20saplings%20on%20weekends.%20Every%20year%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20began%20joining%20him%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20SayTrees%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%