%20must%20be%20created%20for%20stakeholders.%20At%20Merino%20Industries%2C%20this%20is%20done%20sustainably%2C%20maximising%20the%20circular%20economy%20concept%2C%20and%20aligning%20with%20the%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%20These%20principles%20are%20championed%20across%20their%2022%20establishments%2C%20five%20factories%2C%20and%2018%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-1723194932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ponds%20at%20the%20Rohad%20factory%20premises%20are%20a%20sustainable%20addition%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-1723194932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-1723194932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-1723194932-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-1723194932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-7-1723194932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360490%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20ponds%20at%20the%20Rohad%20factory%20premises%20are%20a%20sustainable%20addition.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vermicompost%20beds%20have%20been%20created%20to%20support%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVermicompost%20beds%20have%20been%20created%20to%20support%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20success%20story%20is%20scripted%20in%20how%20over%2075%2C000%20metric%20tons%20of%20GHG%20(greenhouse%20gas)%20or%20tCO2e%20(metric%20tons%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20equivalent)%20emissions%20in%20air%20were%20saved%20in%20the%20reporting%20year%20by%20utilising%20agro-residues%20(biogenic%20fuels)%20instead%20of%20coal%20in%20the%20boilers%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20facilities%20at%20the%20Rohad%20and%20Hapur%20plant%20of%20Merino.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerino%20prides%20itself%20on%20collaborating%20with%20academia%20and%20integrating%20expert%20opinions%20in%20their%20industrial%20processes%2C%20as%20they%20attempt%20to%20align%20with%20sustainable%20goals.%20One%20of%20these%20collaborations%20was%20with%20Visvesvaraya%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(VNIT%2C%20Nagpur).%20The%20latter%20assisted%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20in-house%20expertise%20in%20assessing%20carbon%20footprint%20and%20accreditation%20as%20per%20ISO%20standards%20and%20also%20pitched%20in%20with%20insights%20on%20developing%20circular%20economy%20principle-based%20projects%20of%20the%20Nirmal%20Program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20green%20energy%20proposition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20(February%202024)%20highlighted%20a%20report%20by%20India%20Rating%20and%20Research%2C%20noting%20that%20thermal%20power%20represents%2075%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20power%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20many%20industries%20use%20thermal%20power%20from%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20we%20are%20among%20the%20first%20to%20experiment%20with%20biomass%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Lohia%20notes.%20This%20helps%20Merino%20Industries%20promote%20green%20fuel%20and%20support%20local%20communities%20in%20Hapur%20(Uttar%20Pradesh)%20and%20Rohad%20(Haryana)%20by%20ensuring%20consistent%20demand%20for%20agri-residues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bamboo%20plantation%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20campus%20enhances%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20area%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%