old%20that%20the%20police%20officers%20were%20on%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20he%20watched%20on%20the%20live%20stream%20as%20cops%20entered%20and%20covered%20the%20camera.%20Few%20hours%20later%2C%20Abraham%E2%80%99s%20sister%20posted%20on%20the%20forum%20that%20he%20had%20passed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20has%20made%20its%20way%20onto%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3275718%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20internet%20mediations%20and%20good%20samaritans%20where%20the%2017-year-old%20from%20India%20finds%20mention.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20also%20did%20is%20help%20this%20young%20boy%20find%20his%20purpose%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20others.%20His%20intrinsic%20goodness%20and%20splendid%20effort%20to%20help%20a%20stranger%20living%20in%20a%20faraway%20country%20was%20appreciated%20by%20people%20around%20the%20world%2C%20with%20messages%20pouring%20in.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20got%20it%2C%20I%20never%20understood%20why%20what%20I%20did%20deserved%20so%20much%20praise%20and%20commendation.%20I%20just%20did%20what%20anyone%20else%20should%20have%20done%3B%20what%20the%20very%20first%20person%20who%20saw%20that%20post%20should%20have%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dushyant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20incident%20changed%20the%20young%20boy%20completely%2C%20and%20turned%20him%20into%20a%20compassionate%20teenager%20for%20whom%20helping%20others%20became%20a%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECut%20to%2017%20years%20later%2C%20this%20good%20samaritan%2C%20known%20as%20St%20Broseph%20or%20Batman%20of%20Bengaluru%20on%20Reddit%2C%20has%20helped%20over%205%2C000%20people%20solve%20their%20problems%2C%20ranging%20from%20domestic%20violence%2C%20stalking%2C%20civic%20issues%2C%20theft%2C%20landlord%20woes%20and%20much%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20braved%20death%20threats%2C%20police%20intimidation%20and%20much%20more.%20After%20quitting%20his%20job%20as%20marketing%20manager%20in%20July%202023%2C%20he%20has%20been%20fully%20devoted%20to%20social%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20St%20Broseph%20Foundation%20works%20on%20various%20initiatives%20such%20as%20women%20empowerment%2C%20civic%20and%20legal%20awareness%2C%20mental%20health%20support%2C%20student%20issues%2C%20legal%20support%2C%20career%20counselling%20as%20well%20as%20supporting%20victims%20of%20domestic%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%20also%20runs%20safe%20spaces%20known%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267925%2Fasif-khan-bambooka-bamboo-bicycle-features-cost-ecofriendly-buy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESt%20Broseph%20Safehouses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20fully%20furnished%20apartments%20offering%20free%20accommodation%20and%20security%20to%20victims%20of%20crime%20who%20are%20physically%20at-risk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20has%20over%208%2C000%20volunteers%2C%2015%20chapters%2C%20and%20400%20coordinators%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20with%20volunteers%20based%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Chennai%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBatman%20of%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357495%2Faffordable-meals-outside-hospitals-noida-delhi-ncr-jan-rasoye-vidit-sharma-daily-wagers-humanity-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseeds%20of%20altruism%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20sown%20in%20Dushyant%20by%20his%20father.%20Even%20if%20he%20saw%20a%20punctured%20vehicle%20on%20the%20road%2C%20he%20would%20help%20the%20driver.%20As%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20the%20fundamental%20shift%20in%20his%2