into%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20he%20was%20fueled%20by%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20sacrifice.%20Recognising%20his%20talent%2C%20his%20father%20had%20sold%20their%20cow%20to%20purchase%20a%20hockey%20kit%20for%20young%20Sreejesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20struggle%20had%20just%20begun%20for%20him.%20Sreejesh%20was%20constantly%20mocked%20for%20his%20looks%2C%20traditional%20attire%20(%3Cem%3Eveshti)%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Malayalam%20accent.%20Being%20told%20that%20a%20Kerala%20player%20would%20never%20make%20it%20big%20in%20Indian%20hockey%2C%20there%20were%20times%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20give%20up.%20But%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20sacrifices%20kept%20him%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreejesh%20practised%20day%20and%20night%2C%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Indian%20junior%20hockey%20team.%20He%20won%20three%20Asian%20Games%20medals%2C%20including%20gold%20in%20Hangzhou%202022%2C%20which%20secured%20India%E2%80%99s%20spot%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359575%2Folympics-avinash-sable-india-paris-steeplechase-gold-medal-at-asian-games-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParis%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Named%20FIH%E2%80%99s%20(International%20Hockey%20Federation)%20best%20goalkeeper%20in%202021%20and%202022%2C%20he%20silenced%20his%20critics%20with%20his%20stellar%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hindustan%20Times%20article%20mentioned%20that%20Sreejesh%20believes%20a%20goalkeeper%20should%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98crazy%20person%E2%80%99%20and%20must%20know%20the%20art%20of%20intimidating.%20%E2%80%9CCrazy%2C%20because%20you%20just%20need%20to%20have%20the%20guts%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20that%20ball.%20The%20second%20thing%20is%20aggression%3B%20you%20need%20to%20be%20an%20aggressive%20person%2C%20and%20those%20reflexes%20have%20to%20be%20there.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20much%20time%20to%20just%20think%2C%20%E2%80%98Save%E2%80%99.%20No%2C%20you%20just%20need